added.title: That's a Wrap
added.description: Duncan goes on a mission to scare Courtney during a field trip to the museum.

added.title: Tiger Fail
added.description: Gwen refuses to be pressured into choosing an ice cream flavor that she does not want.

added.title: A Ninjustice to Harold
added.description: Harold's world is turned upside down when Beth becomes the class ninja.

added.title: #AllyCat Part 1
added.description: When Zee Zatara realizes Lex Luthor has unearthed a magical book with the power to tell the future, the girls reluctantly enlist Catwoman to help them steal it from him before he understands what he has, but it may already be too late.

added.title: #AllyCat Part 2
added.description: When Zee Zatara realizes Lex Luthor has unearthed a magical book with the power to tell the future, the girls reluctantly enlist Catwoman to help them steal it from him before he understands what he has, but it may already be too late.

added.title: #Retreat!
added.description: Jessica Cruz and some super friends go on an overnight camping trip without their powers and are attacked by Poison Ivy and a horde of Plant Zombies!

added.title: Wednesday - Part 3
added.description: Elliott and his mom Frankie are about to have a Wednesday they'll never forget, when a mysterious rock unexpectedly transports them somewhere across the universe. Finding themselves in a strange new environment with strange new creatures, they meet a dinosaur named Mo - and that's just the beginning of their out of this world adventure!

added.title: Wednesday - Part 4
added.description: Elliott and his mom Frankie are about to have a Wednesday they'll never forget, when a mysterious rock unexpectedly transports them somewhere across the universe. Finding themselves in a strange new environment with strange new creatures, they meet a dinosaur named Mo - and that's just the beginning of their out of this world adventure!

added.title: Cat Burglar
added.description: While Tiggy and Boss work hard to cover their tracks after they're caught up in a cat burglary, a new churro cart catches Gweeseek's eye.

added.title: The Fanciest Fungie
added.description: Seth, frustrated that the Fancies are too caught up in the Fanciest Fancy pageant to listen to his warning about a fungus-eating bacteria, enters the pageant to get his message out. But when he gets sucked into the pageant, he'll have to face the consequences of getting distracted.

added.title: Snake It to the Limit
added.description: When Seth agrees to let an athletic snake replace his arm so he can finally be good at volleyball, he learns he doesn't need a fancy snake arm to make his teammates happy; he just needs to try.

added.title: Nevin's Cocoon
added.description: After a beautiful statue makes Nevin self-conscious about his own looks, Seth helps seal Nevin in a cocoon so that he may turn into a beautiful butterfly.

added.title: Cool Kids
added.description: When Pascal becomes obsessed with a group of cool kids, Seth promises to use his science skills to help Pascal become cool. But is coolness as cool as it seems?

added.title: Mini Mongor
added.description: The Thunderkittens unleash a demon who is powered by fear. Too bad he's small and not that scary.

added.title: Swampy Johnny
added.description: The Thundercats invite a super cool swamp man into the Cat's Lair who is on the run from some scary looking aliens!

added.title: Tygra's Garden
added.description: Tygra says he's done being a Thundercat after he gets engaged to a sentient flower. Now it's up to Lion-O to break up the wedding!

added.title: The Space Beam
added.description: The new rulers of Plun-Darr say they'll bring one of the Mutants home; whichever one of them activates a homing beacon that will blow up the Thundercats. Now it's every Mutant for themselves as they battle it out to be the one to activate the beacon!

added.title: Plundsmas
added.description:
The Mutants refuse to celebrate their favorite holiday, Plunds-Mas, now that Plun-Darr is gone. So now it's up to the Thundercats to raise their spirits by enacting the
eight horrors of Plunds-Mas!

added.title: The Glitch
added.description: In order to stop Unagami the ninja must obtain three Key-tanas, the first of which is hidden in the game zone Terra Kerana, one of Prime Empire's most dangerous game environments.

added.title: The Cliffs of Hysteria
added.description: While being chased by Unagami's dreaded Red Visors the ninja must climb the 'Cliffs of Hysteria', however, they make a startling discovery: Unagami is converting players into energy cubes in order to build a portal into the real world!

added.title: The Maze of the Red Dragon
added.description: Still in the game zone Terra Kerana, the Samurai guide Okino has to choose between helping his allies the ninja, or obeying the evil orders of his Master, Unagami.

added.title: One Step Forward, Two Steps Back
added.description: When the ninja learn that the only way to acquire the second Key-tana is by winning a dangerous race in Terra Technica they'll have to find some racing cars in unexpected ways.

added.title: Racer Seven
added.description: As the ninja prepare for the brutal Speedway Five-Billion race, Lloyd meets a race driver named Seven, who is programmed to lose, but who may hold the key to victory.

added.title: Unboxing Part 1
added.description: Axel ventures into his uncle's strictly off-limits basement lab in hopes of fixing a broken toy and ends up unleashing living ones instead: the renegade Madcap and a whole team of superpowered toys dedicated to stopping him!

added.title: Unboxing Part 2
added.description: Axel discovers that he can transform into a toy and teams up with his new team of toys to stop Madcap from stealing a Minergy battery.

added.title: Attack of Thermometron 9000
added.description: Axel must wrangle Galileo and Bobbie to shut down a rogue thermostat - improperly upgraded by Slobot - as it plunges the house into extreme hot and cold zones.

added.title: The Dynamo Dynamic
added.description: Axel finds himself at the center of a disagreement between Sarge and Masko over what's more important in battle - the weapon or the one who wields it - after Dynamo bonds the trio together!

added.title: Access Denied
added.description: When Axel and the team try to figure out what Sarge Charge's secret weapon is, they get ejected from the house by his newly upgraded security system and must fight their way back inside before Madcap does.

added.title: The Bakugan Battle League Dash/The Final Stage
added.description: The Bakugan Battle League Dash: With Dan and Ajit eliminated from the Bakugan Battle League - Tokyo Edition, the remaining Awesome Brawlers - Shun, Wynton, Lia and Lightning race to complete the second stage of the competition. In order to make it to the final stage, the gang will have to pull together to defeat some tough competition./The Final Stage: It's the final stage of the Bakugan Battle League Tokyo Edition! The remaining Awesome Brawlers are ready to go, but just as the final round begins, the competitors are surprised with some unwelcome guests.

added.title: The Tokyo Catastrophe/Bakugan Battle League Finale
added.description: The Tokyo Catastrophe: Haavik has highjacked the Bakugan Battle league - Tokyo Edition! He's been using the tournament as a platform for his sinister plot to bring chaos and destruction to the city of Tokyo./Bakugan Battle League Finale: Haavik unleashes an army of unruly Bakugan to bring his own brand of chaos and destruction to the city of Tokyo. It's all hands-on-deck to stop the invasion, and foil Haavik's plot.

added.title: Champion of the Universe, Dan!/Operation Babysitter
added.description: Champion of the Universe, Dan!: Dan starts "sleep brawling", rolling out Drago causing damage and confusion while he's fast asleep. With the help of a "sleep expert", Ajit attempts to stop Dan and put his "sleep brawling" to rest once and for all./Operation Babysitter: Ajit lands a job babysitting a rambunctious toddler - Aiden. Having no experience with kids, Ajit recruits Wynton to help him out. Things get a little out of hand when Aiden rolls out - Krakelious. Now, Ajit and Wynton have a tiny Baku-brawler on their hands, with no way to stop him!

added.title: Beastie Team Battle/Ajit and Lia
added.description: Beastie Team Battle: China Riot is on the lookout for a partner to team up with in the new Bakugan battle team tournament being held in Los Volmos. Riot may have only been after a brawling partner, but ends up with a new friend./Ajit and Lia: Lia knows the story of where Ajit found his Golden Baku-balls, but no one knows "how" he's able to partner with Golden Bakugan. To get the inside scoop, Lia tags along with Ajit at his new job as a security guard at the local Museum.

added.title: Once More into the Maze/Grandpas in the Wild
added.description: Once More into the Maze: Storm, McQ, Sophie and Everett were spotted at the ruins where the great core cell is housed! Alarmed by the report from Benton Dusk, the Awesome Brawlers head to the Yucatan Peninsula to investigate./Grandpas in the Wild: During an all-out brawl with Storm, McQ, Sophie and Everett, the Awesome Brawlers are hit with an attack that sends everyone spiraling to various parts of the maze. Split up from the rest of the gang, Wynton and Lightning find themselves in a strange unfamiliar part of the maze. While trying to get their bearings, they discover some new golden allies.

added.title: #CenaParaCinco
added.description: Barbara Gordon está en apuros cuando una cena incómoda el padre de una nueva amiga, se convierte en algo muy diferente.
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: Los Acantilados de la Histeria
added.description: Los Ninjas suben a los Acantilados de la histeria y descubren que Unagami convierte a los jugadores en cubos de energía para construir un portal.

added.title: La Falla
added.description: Para detener a Unagami, los Ninjas debe obtener 3 Keytanas, la primera está escondida en Tierra Karana, uno de los entornos de juego más peligrosos.

added.title: Un Paso Adelante, Dos Pasos Atras
added.description: La única manera de que los Ninjas obtengan segunda Keytana es ganando una carrera en Tierra Technica y tiene que conseguir autos de carreras para eso.

added.title: Piloto Siete
added.description: Mientras los Ninjas se preparan para la carrera Cinco Billones por Hora, Lloyd conoce a la Piloto Siete quien puede tener la clave de la victoria.

added.title: El Laberinto del Dragon Rojo
added.description: Aún en la zona de juego de Tierra Karana, Okino tiene que elegir entre ayudar a sus aliados ninjas, u obedecer las órdenes de su Maestro, Unagami.

added.title: Show de momias
added.description: Duncan sale en una misión para espantar a Courtney durante una excursión al museo.

added.title: Fallo de tigre
added.description: Gwen se niega a que la presionen para elegir un sabor de helado que no quiere.

added.title: Una ninja justicia para Harold
added.description: El mundo de Harold queda de cabeza cuando sus compañeros declaran que Beth es la verdadera ninja de la clase.

added.title: #Retirada
added.description: Jessica Cruz y algunas de sus mejores amigas salen a pasar una noche de campamento sin sus poderes, iy son atacadas por Hiedra Venenosa y una horda de plantas zombis!
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: #GatoCallejero Parte 1
added.description: Cuando Zee Zatara se da cuenta de que Lex Luthor desenterró un libro mágico que tiene el poder de predecir el futuro, las chicas le piden ayuda a Gatúbela para robárselo antes de que Lex comprenda lo que tiene en su poder. Pero puede que ya sea demasiado tarde...
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: #GatoCallejero Parte 2
added.description: Cuando Zee Zatara se da cuenta de que Lex Luthor desenterró un libro mágico que tiene el poder de predecir el futuro, las chicas le piden ayuda a Gatúbela para robárselo antes de que Lex comprenda lo que tiene en su poder. Pero puede que ya sea demasiado tarde...
added.originalseriesname: DC Super Hero Girls en Espanol

added.title: La Dinamica del Dinamo
added.description: iAxel se encuentra en el centro de un desacuerdo entre Sarge y Masko sobre lo que es más importante en la batalla, el arma o el que lo maneja, después de que Dynamo une al trío!

added.title: Unboxing Parte 1
added.description: Axel se aventura en el laboratorio de sótano estrictamente prohibido de su tío con la esperanza de arreglar un juguete roto y termina desatando a los vivos: iel renegado Madcap y todo un equipo de juguetes superpoderosos dedicados a detenerlo!

added.title: Acceso Denegado
added.description: Cuando Axel y el equipo intentan descubrir cuál es el arma secreta de Sarge Charge, son expulsados ​​de la casa por su sistema de seguridad recientemente actualizado y deben abrirse camino antes de que Madcap lo haga.

added.title: Ataque de Thermometron 9000
added.description: Axel debe lidiar con Galileo y Bobbie para apagar un termostato deshonesto, que Slobot actualizó incorrectamente, ya que sumerge la casa en zonas extremadamente frías y calientes.

added.title: Unboxing Parte 2
added.description: Axel descubre que puede transformarse en un juguete y se une a su nuevo equipo de juguetes para evitar que Madcap robe una batería de Minergy.
